Instance OR vm (virtual machine) is a virtual server that contain cpu,memory,
disk and network, also include with some additional services like firewall etc..
		
  
*Features in Fogpanel Instance are:*
		
# Scale cpu and memory
		
# Attach iso's
		
# Add secondary disks
		
# Backup Instance
		
# Firewall
		
# Password reset
		
# Instance Action like start,stop etc..
		
# Aquire/release secondary ip
		
# Ssh-key security
		
# Secure console access
		
# Vm-statics (like cpu,bandwidth etc..)
	
